                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d300">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Statement Released by the Department of State, October 10,
                        1947</hi>
                    <note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d300fn4">Reprinted from Department of State
                            <hi rend="italic">Bulletin</hi>, October 19, 1947, p. 778.</note>
                </head>
                <dateline>
                    <date ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-document-head" calendar="gregorian"
                        when="1947-10-10">October 10, 1947</date>
                </dateline>
                <p>The attention of the Department of State has been drawn to published rumors that
                    the United States is sponsoring the merger of the Greek and Turkish General
                    Staffs.</p>
                <p>The Department categorically denies that there is any basis whatsoever for such
                    rumors.</p>
            </div>
